PROJECT.NAME: heTriNodu
PROJECT.TITLE: Triaenophorus nodulosus
PROJECT.DESCRIPTION: This project collects the sequencing data and assemblies generated for Triaenophorus nodulosus by the European Reference Genome Atlas (ERGA, https://www.erga-biodiversity.eu/) for the Biodiversity Genomics Europe project (BGE, https://biodiversitygenomics.eu/).
